snippet.title: Best VGM 1853 - Tales of Zestiria - The Melody of Water Will Lead the Way
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / PS4 / PS3
Tales of Zestiria (2015)
The Melody of Water Will Lead the Way
Go Shiina
